This requires a local version of latest perl:

wget http://www.cpan.org/src/5.0/perl-5.18.0.tar.gz
tar xf perl-5.18.0.tar.gz
cd perl-5.18.0
mkdir /root/perl
./Configure -des -Dprefix=/root/perl
make && make install

Install modules:
/root/perl/bin/cpan -i WWW::Mechanize
/root/perl/bin/cpan -i File::Find::Rule
